  "description": "Add Polish Translation for \"Image unavailable\" Message\n\nEnsure the \"Image unavailable\" text is properly translated to Polish and configured in the application's translation system.\n\nRequirements:\n- Locate all instances of \"Image unavailable\" text in the codebase\n- Add Polish translation key to the translation configuration file\n- Provide accurate Polish translation (e.g., \"Obraz niedostępny\")\n- Replace hardcoded \"Image unavailable\" strings with translation keys\n- Verify translation appears correctly when Polish locale is selected\n- Ensure translation follows existing translation file structure and naming conventions\n- Test that fallback to English works if translation is missing",
